{
  "stem": "5356.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When the Russians started approaching closer by, they took us into the boxcars, and they transported us to Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Czestochowa, we worked for the same company, for HASAG.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had factories there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- some of the-- the people, when we came there, were shipped directly to Leipzig, Germany to factories.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some of them stayed there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and one day, they came and they said that if somebody's got friends or relatives on another camp in the same city-- we were in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it so happened that my brother from Sandomierz-- in Liceum, from that camp-- was shipped to Czestochowa to the Czestochowianka, it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we changed and went over to be together with our third brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Schmuel Meir.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we moved over to that place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a new camp they had just built for repairing tanks and things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Czestochowianka, like the same name as the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you know, it's-- like you would say Los Angelinos or something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the way Czestochowa and Czestochowianka-- that was the name of the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were there, in Czestochowianka, til about January the 16, I think, when the Russians were over bombarding the city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's when they marched us out of camp to the train and put us into boxcars and shipped to Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It took us three days to arrive in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just-- we just-- while we were still at the station, we could hear the explosions from the-- from the-- what the Russians were bombarding the city.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, we were locked up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I mean, the SS was around the-- the wagons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they shipped us.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
